@startuml
title Open Data Agent Workbench - AG-UI Agent Runtime Architecture

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor "Frontend\nCopilotKit / AG-UI Client" as Frontend

node "apps/api\nSingle HTTP Runtime" as Api {
  component "POST /api/copilotkit" as CopilotEndpoint
  component "DataAgentAgUiAgent\nextends AbstractAgent" as AgUiAgent
  component "RunInput Mapper\nthreadId/runId/context/state/forwardedProps" as RunInput
}

package "Agent Runtime" as AgentRuntime {
  component "@ag-ui/mastra\nMastraAgent" as AgUiMastra
  component "Mastra DataAgent\nReAct + tool calling" as DataAgent
  component "Tool Registry\nsrc/tools/" as ToolRegistry
  component "AG-UI Event Helpers\nACTIVITY / CUSTOM" as EventHelpers
}

package "Data Boundary" as DataBoundary {
  component "Data Gateway\ninternal TypeScript API" as DataGateway
  component "SQL Guard\nreadonly + limit + timeout" as SqlGuard
  database "Datasources\nDuckDB demo / SQLite / CSV / XLSX" as Datasources
}

package "Persistence" as Persistence {
  database "Metadata SQLite\none DB per storage path" as Metadata
  component "Run Events\nappend-only AG-UI BaseEvent" as RunEvents
  component "SQL Audit Logs" as SqlAudit
  component "Artifact Service\nTable result preview" as Artifacts
  component "Knowledge Boundary\ncollections / chunks / retrieval" as Knowledge
}

cloud "LLM Provider\nOpenAI-compatible or Mastra router" as Provider

Frontend --> CopilotEndpoint : AG-UI request
CopilotEndpoint --> AgUiAgent : route dataAgent
AgUiAgent --> RunInput : extract run context
AgUiAgent --> Metadata : create session/run
AgUiAgent --> AgUiMastra : delegate RunAgentInput
AgUiMastra --> DataAgent : stream agent run
DataAgent --> Provider : model stream
DataAgent --> ToolRegistry : inspect_schema / run_sql_readonly
ToolRegistry --> EventHelpers : create ACTIVITY_SNAPSHOT / ACTIVITY_DELTA / CUSTOM
EventHelpers --> AgUiAgent : emit AG-UI events
AgUiAgent --> RunEvents : persist same events
AgUiAgent --> Frontend : stream same AG-UI events

ToolRegistry --> DataGateway : inspect schema / run readonly SQL
DataGateway --> Metadata : validate datasource ownership
DataGateway --> SqlGuard : enforce SQL policy
SqlGuard --> Datasources : allowed read query
DataGateway --> SqlAudit : write audit result
DataGateway --> Artifacts : create table artifact
Artifacts --> Metadata : persist artifact metadata
Knowledge ..> ToolRegistry : future retrieve_knowledge tool

note right of RunEvents
Persisted event types are AG-UI EventType only.
No custom frontend protocol events.
end note

note bottom of Metadata
Default grain:
METADATA_DB_PATH=storage/metadata/workbench.sqlite
Tables are isolated by user_id/session_id/run_id.
end note

@enduml
